The current year interim results (half yearly report for 2010) <ref>http://www.piac.com.pk/PIA_About/profiles/2010/PIA-Half-Yearly-Report-2010_21092010.pdf</ref> do not show any improvement in profitability. The after tax losses reported for the first six months of 2010 are PKR 6.90 billion as compared to PKR 5.39 billion for the first six months of 2009. Revenue, however, did increase to PKR 49.31 billion for the first half of 2010 compared with PKR 41.92 billion for the first half of 2009.

Passenger traffic has been more or less static over the last five years hovering around the five and a half million mark with a load factor of around 70%.

